    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Asphalt obtained from the refining of petroleum; the heavier or more viscous portions of certain crude oils are asphalts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
